:0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"록","body":"혹시, 무슨 해결책이라도 생각나셨나요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"serious01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event187-05-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"파레오","body":"네…… 발할라의 팬들을 설득하고 싶은데\nRAS의 파레오네가 무슨 말을 해도\n이야기를 들어주지 않겠죠.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event187-05-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"파레오","body":"그렇다면, 이야기를 들어줄 만한 사람에게\n설득을 부탁할 수 없을지 생각했거든요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event187-05-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"록","body":"이야기를 들어줄 만한 사람……\n앗! 발할라의 멤버…… 특히 사키 씨라면!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event187-05-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontS